short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Download completed FormSquared.com forms as PDFs.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Easily download completed FormSquared.com forms as cleanly formatted PDF files.

✅ Clean implementation: no toolbar button or popup required. FormSquared to PDF automatically adds a Download button to each form to streamline the download process.

✅ Avoid cluttered PDFs: removes unnecessary clutter from the form before downloading to create readable PDF files.

✅ Automatic file names: saves time and helps identify your downloaded form more easily. v1.1 now adds dates to filenames for even easier identification.



⚠️ Note: Chrome will use your default download settings to save the PDF. To learn how to change these visit: https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95759

This extension was created by a third party, and is not associated with FormSquared in any way.
